songs.title: I Don’t Need
songs.lyrics:
[Chorus: Young Chop]
Taking trips overseas
Make a bad bitch get on her knees
All that bullshit, I don't need
Keep a big bankroll on me

[Verse 1: Young Chop]
Hit up Fendi, bought a lot of it
Niggas hating, that's some sucker shit
If the bitch bad, I'ma buy the bitch
And my diamonds drippin' like water faucets
Niggas better be cautious, I got a forty
Hit the trap house, then place your order
Nigga mad 'cause I'm fuckin' on his daughter
You can have her back, I don't even really want her

[Pre-Chorus: Young Chop]
I don't even want her, yeah (I don't even want her)
You can have her back, I don't really even want her
I don't even want her (I don't even want her)
You can have her back, I don't really even want her, yeah

[Chorus: Young Chop]
Taking trips overseas
Make a bad bitch get on her knees
All that bullshit, I don't need
Keep a big bankroll on me

[Verse 2: Rizzo]
Eating sunflowers while I'm feeding your girl all my seeds, yeah
Green be the lane, like, all this paper in my jeans, yeah
I be too damn geeked, pills got me acting like a fiend, huh
Bitch, pay the fee, nothing in my life was ever free
Overseas, collecting all this paper
I'm on a route, I'll see you later

[Chorus: Young Chop]
Taking trips overseas
Make a bad bitch get on her knees
All that bullshit, I don't need
Keep a big bankroll on me
